本协议提供中文与英文两个文本版本，二者意在保持含义一致并相互对应。
如因排版、翻译或笔误导致两种文本出现不一致，应以能够最大程度协调两种
文本、并最符合本协议整体目的与条款体系的解释为准；该类不一致不应被解释
为授予用户任何额外权利或对版权持有人施加任何额外义务。版权持有人可随时
发布更正版本以消除不一致。
This Agreement is provided in both Chinese and English, and both texts are
intended to be meaningfully identical and mutually corresponding. If any
inconsistency arises due to formatting, translation, or clerical errors,
the interpretation that best reconciles both texts and best reflects the
overall purpose and structure of this Agreement shall apply; and such
inconsistency shall not be construed to grant the User any additional
rights or impose any additional obligations on the copyright holder. The
copyright holder may publish a corrected version at any time to eliminate
any inconsistency.

